Day 44: Write a Docker Compose File

Date: October 10, 2025
Overview
Created multi-container applications using Docker Compose.
Key Concepts Learned

Docker Compose syntax (YAML)
Service definitions
Volume and network management
Environment variables

Commands Used
yamlversion: '3'
services:
  web:
    image: nginx
    ports:
      - "80:80"
  db:
    image: mysql:5.7
    environment:
      MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD: password
bashdocker-compose up -d
docker-compose down
Challenges Faced
YAML indentation errors! One wrong space breaks everything.

Day 45: Resolve Dockerfile Issues
Date: October 10, 2025
Overview
Debugged and fixed problematic Dockerfiles.
Key Concepts Learned

Build troubleshooting
Error log analysis
Dependency resolution
Best practices enforcement

Commands Used
bashdocker build --no-cache -t image:tag .
docker logs container_name
docker inspect container_name
Challenges Faced
Build failures due to network issues, missing dependencies, and syntax errors. Learned to read build output carefully!
